On May 2, 2004, at 4:48 PM, Sage Green wrote:

> Question: where does the vacuum line on the EGR valve go to??  I have 
> just 3/4 of the line connected to the EGR valve, and I cannot find 
> where it should connect at the other end; it is cut too short, and I 
> cannot see an empty connector.  I will have a major leak,  Help!!

EGR valve vacuum hose connects to a 4-way on the manifold vacuum line.  
(It can be just a tee if you don't have a distributor that has a retard 
side).

